150
00:08:25.085 --> 00:08:27.244
<font color="cyan">You know how it works.</font>
Yeah...

151
00:08:29.804 --> 00:08:31.604
<font color="cyan">Ludo and I might be away.</font>

152
00:08:31.645 --> 00:08:32.805
<font color="cyan">Did I say?</font>

153
00:08:32.845 --> 00:08:34.284
<font color="cyan">For Christmas.</font>

154
00:08:34.325 --> 00:08:35.884
<font color="cyan">Cortina d'Ampezzo.</font>

155
00:08:37.205 --> 00:08:38.764
Skiing...

156
00:08:38.805 --> 00:08:40.205
Nice.

157
00:08:42.045 --> 00:08:44.165
<font color="cyan">It won't always be this way.</font>

158
00:08:44.205 --> 00:08:46.965
Well. we will have to tell him
