These things happen.

163
00:08:57.205 --> 00:08:59.124
It's nobody's fault.

164
00:08:59.165 --> 00:09:00.604
<font color="cyan">It's funny.</font>

165
00:09:01.725 --> 00:09:03.725
<font color="cyan">I think it's you he'd mind losing...</font>

166
00:09:03.764 --> 00:09:05.604
<font color="cyan">far more than me.</font>

167
00:09:10.325 --> 00:09:11.925
SHE LAUGHS

168
00:09:13.325 --> 00:09:14.845
SHE KISSES HIM

169
00:10:08.325 --> 00:10:09.805
TELEPHONE RINGS

170
00:10:09.845 --> 00:10:11.644
<font color="#008000">I'm sure you'll have made plans of</font>
<font color="#008000">your own.</font>

171
00:10:11.685 --> 00:10:14.165
<font color="#008000">but you're very welcome to have</font>
<font color="#008000">Christmas lunch here with us.</font>

172
00:10:14.205 --> 00:10:16.925
<font color="yellow">Oh. you're here. are you?</font>
<font color="yellow">I didn't hear you come in.</font>

173
00:10:16.965 --> 00:10:18.325
